data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven nestled in the heart of Jacksonville. Boasting a prime location, 5776 Birds Nest Ln offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and suburban tranquility.

Upon entry, be greeted by an open-concept living space adorned with contemporary finishes and an abundance of natural light. The well-appointed kitchen features sleek appliances and ample counter space, making it a delightful space for culinary enthusiasts.

The master bedroom serves as a private retreat with its spacious layout and an ensuite bathroom, providing a peaceful sanctuary after a long day. The additional bedrooms are generously sized, offering versatility for a growing family or guests. 

The home offers a new roof, newer HVAC, updated kitchen and bathrooms! Step outside to the backyard where the sounds of nature invite you out on to the patio for your morning coffee or evening cocktail. 

Conveniently located, 5776 Birds Nest Ln is close to schools, parks, and everyday amenities. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways, offering a seamless journey to downtown Jacksonville and surrounding areas.

This property not only provides a comfortable living space but also the opportunity to become part of a vibrant community. Don't miss the chance to call 5776 Birds Nest Ln home. Schedule a showing today and envision your lifestyle in this delightful Jacksonville residence.
